description: A glen in Perthshire, approximately four miles in length, that follows the River Farg.
place_note: Visited before returning to Kehl, Germany.
Stayed while carriage was searched by customs.
Stoped to dine but was so impressed stayed overnight.
Came to look at the Cathtedral and Citadel.

description: A town on the boarder of France and Belgium
place_note: Stoped here to show passports as group entered Belgium.
